cat << EOF
Yet Another Framebuffer Terminal (aka "yaft") is simple terminal emulator for
minimalist. Features:
  various framebuffer types (8/15/16/24/32bpp)
  compatible with vt102 and Linux console (detail)
  UTF-8 encoding and UCS2 gylphs
  256 colors (same as xterm)
  wallpaper
  DRCS (DECDLD/DRCSMMv1) (experimental)
  sixel (experimental).
EOF
